high_descs: Turn around and walk over to the white desk on your right.
Pick up the blue pencil off of the white desk.
Look up at the shelf behind the desk.
Put the blue pencil on the shelf with the golden statue on it.
Walk over to the tall white dresser next to the bed on your right.
Pick up the blue pencil off of the dresser.
Turn around and walk back over to the shelf behind the white desk.
Put the blue pencil on the shelf with the golden statue

high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the bed, turn right, go forward, turn right to the right side of the desk, go to the desk.
Take the blue pencil from the desk.
Stay at the desk.
Put the pencil on the shelf with the gold sculpture.
Turn right, go forward to the dresser to the left of the bed.
Take the blue pencil from the dresser.
Turn around, go back to the right side of the desk.

high_descs: Turn around, then right and face the desk to your right.
